{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-12","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cafe-menu","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 12","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada je potrebno uključiti fajl <code>styles.css</code>, ili ponovo koristiti stilove. Unutar elementa <code>head</code>, dodajte element <code>link</code>. Postavite atribut elementu <code>rel</code> sa vrednošću <code>\"stylesheet\"</code> i atribut elementu <code>href</code> sa vrednošću <code>\"styles.css\"</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Element sa <code>link</code> je element bez zatvarajućeg taga, što znači da nema zatvarački tag. Elementi bez zatvarajućeg taga treba da se pišu kao <code>&#x3C;link></code> umesto <code>&#x3C;link>&#x3C;/link></code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5f3477cb2e27333b1ab2b955","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-12"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <title>Cafe Menu</title>\n    \n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CAMPER CAFE</h1>\n      <p>Est. 2020</p>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Coffee</h2>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[5,7],"history":["index.html"]},{"fileKey":"stylescss","ext":"css","name":"styles","contents":"h1, h2, p {\n  text-align: center;\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["styles.css"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod mora imati komponentu od <code>link</code>.</p>","testString":"const link = document.querySelector('link');\nassert.isNotNull(link);"},{"text":"<p>Element <code>link</code> je element koji nema zatvorni tag, ne bi trebalo da ima zatvorni tag <code>&#x3C;/link></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(code, /<\\/link>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Ne smete da menjate vaš deo sa sadržajem <code>head</code> koji se nalazi. Proverite da niste izbrisali oznaku za zatvaranje.</p>","testString":"const headElementCount = document.querySelectorAll('head')?.length;\nassert.strictEqual(headElementCount, 1);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da ima jedan element <code>link</code>.</p>","testString":"const linkElementCount = document.querySelectorAll('link')?.length;\nassert.strictEqual(linkElementCount, 1);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj element <code>link</code> treba da bude unutar tvog elementa <code>head</code>.</p>","testString":"const link = document.querySelector('head > link');\nassert.isNotNull(link);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element od <code>link</code> mora imati svojstvo elementa <code>rel</code> sa vrednošću <code>stylesheet</code>.</p>","testString":"const linkRelValue = document.querySelector('link')?.getAttribute('rel');\nassert.strictEqual(linkRelValue, 'stylesheet');"},{"text":"<p>Element vašeg <code>link</code> treba da ima svojstvo polja <code>href</code> sa vrednošću <code>styles.css</code>.</p>","testString":"const linkHrefValue = document.querySelector('link')?.dataset?.href;\nassert.strictEqual(linkHrefValue, 'styles.css');\n"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-cafe-menu","dashedName":"step-12","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"css","module":"basic-css","block":"workshop-cafe-menu","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-13","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-11","id":"5f3477cb2e27333b1ab2b955","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Cafe Menu</title>\n    <link href=\"styles.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"menu\">\n      <main>\n        <h1>CAMPER CAFE</h1>\n        <p class=\"established\">Est. 2020</p>\n        <hr>\n        <section>\n          <h2>Coffee</h2>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-cafe/coffee.jpg\" alt=\"coffee icon\"/>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"flavor\">French Vanilla</p><p class=\"price\">3.00</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"flavor\">Caramel Macchiato</p><p class=\"price\">3.75</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"flavor\">Pumpkin Spice</p><p class=\"price\">3.50</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"flavor\">Hazelnut</p><p class=\"price\">4.00</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"flavor\">Mocha</p><p class=\"price\">4.50</p>\n          </article>\n        </section>\n        <section>\n          <h2>Desserts</h2>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-cafe/pie.jpg\" alt=\"pie icon\"/>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"dessert\">Donut</p><p class=\"price\">1.50</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"dessert\">Cherry Pie</p><p class=\"price\">2.75</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"dessert\">Cheesecake</p><p class=\"price\">3.00</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"item\">\n            <p class=\"dessert\">Cinnamon Roll</p><p class=\"price\">2.50</p>\n          </article>\n        </section>\n      </main>\n      <hr class=\"bottom-line\">\n      <footer>\n        <address>\n          <p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\" target=\"_blank\">Visit our website</a>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"address\">123 Free Code Camp Drive</p>\n        </address>\n      </footer>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"},{"name":"styles","ext":"css","contents":"body {\n  background-image: url(https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-cafe/beans.jpg);\n  font-family: sans-serif;\n  padding: 20px;\n}\n\nh1 {\n  font-size: 40px;\n  margin-top: 0;\n  margin-bottom: 15px;\n}\n\nh2 {\n  font-size: 30px;\n}\n\n.established {\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n\nh1, h2, p {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.menu {\n  width: 80%;\n  background-color: burlywood;\n  margin-left: auto;\n  margin-right: auto;\n  padding: 20px;\n  max-width: 500px;\n}\n\nimg {\n  display: block;\n  margin-left: auto;\n  margin-right: auto;\n  margin-top: -25px;\n}\n\nhr {\n  height: 2px;\n  background-color: brown;\n  border-color: brown;\n}\n\n.bottom-line {\n  margin-top: 25px;\n}\n\nh1, h2 {\n  font-family: Impact, serif;\n}\n\n.item p {\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin-top: 5px;\n  margin-bottom: 5px;\n  font-size: 18px;\n}\n\n.flavor, .dessert {\n  text-align: left;\n  width: 75%;\n}\n\n.price {\n  text-align: right;\n  width: 25%;\n}\n\n/* FOOTER */\n\nfooter {\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\n\naddress {\n  font-style: normal;\n}\n\n.address {\n  margin-bottom: 5px;\n}\n\na {\n  color: black;\n}\n\na:visited {\n  color: black;\n}\n\na:hover {\n  color: brown;\n}\n\na:active {\n  color: brown;\n}","history":["styles.css"],"fileKey":"stylescss"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-12"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}